Donald James ELKINS et al. v. NEW MEXICO AND ARIZONA LAND COMPANY et al. No. 5371. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. Aug. 3, 1956. Bart W. O’Hara, Denver, Colo., Charles A. Murdock, Denver, Colo., and Robertson & Skinner, Raton, N. M., for appellants. J. R. Modrall, and William C. Briggs, Albuquerque, N. M., for appellees.

Before BRATTON, Chief Judge.

Dismissed on motion of appellants, ap-pellees consenting thereto. D.C., 137 F. Supp. 767.
